{"tid":1878923,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華府再為美企提供45日寬限期　以便繼續與華為交易","createTime":"2020-02-14T01:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T01:20:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2d1e1c0013c89d30ee2f4c42793428271ed69469","tid":1878923,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1508473_1_L_20200214073540.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1508473_1_L_20200214073540.jpg&h=e35ea139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國政府再為當地通訊企業提供45日的寬限期，以便企業可以繼續與中國電訊設備生產商華為進行交易。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部在聲明中表示，寬限期將為特別是農村地區的電訊供應商，可以繼續臨時營運現有網絡，並在寬限期間尋找替代。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部加控中國電訊設備生產商華為、副董事長孟晚舟及美國兩間子公司，竊取商業秘密等16項新罪名。檢察官指控華為等企業，從六家美國的科技公司竊取知識產權，以獲得不公平的競爭優勢。起訴書同時指控華為涉嫌違反禁制令，與被美國制裁的伊朗及北韓等國家有生意往來。"},{"pid":"51c415a9ad7b1ec19dd31388b17466f7da662a6a","tid":1878923,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Huawei-01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2FHuawei-01.png&h=a771d838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5dc423205272b81167ca1f64.jpg/o4l5fSpvLSWnQaZg5nCwHwxkOpkXPUdGCr0IIAq9CCA?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5dc423205272b81167ca1f64.jpg%2Fo4l5fSpvLSWnQaZg5nCwHwxkOpkXPUdGCr0IIAq9CCA%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=c60a1e71&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}